## FILE NAMING

| Type | Format | Example |
|------|--------|---------|
| Entity | `[name].entity.ts` | `user.entity.ts` |
| Value Object | `[name].value-object.ts` | `email.value-object.ts` |
| Aggregate | `[name].aggregate.ts` | `order.aggregate.ts` |
| Use Case | `[action]-[entity].use-case.ts` | `create-user.use-case.ts` |
| Command | `[action]-[entity].command.ts` | `create-user.command.ts` |
| Query | `[action]-[entity].query.ts` | `get-user.query.ts` |
| Port | `[name].[type].port.ts` | `user.repository.port.ts` |
| Domain Event | `[entity]-[past-action].event.ts` | `user-created.event.ts` |
| Controller | `[name].controller.ts` | `user.controller.ts` |
| Repository | `[name].repository.[impl].ts` | `user.repository.postgres.ts` |
| Service | `[name]-[provider].service.ts` | `email-sendgrid.service.ts` |
| Result | `result.ts` | `shared/result/result.ts` |

